---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Best Dog Food by Breed UK (2026) — Every Breed Guide in One Place"
description: "Browse our breed-by-breed dog food guides for the UK. Find the best food for your breed's specific needs, plus puppy and senior feeding guides where available."
permalink: "/best-dog-food-by-breed/"
---

{# Each display group can absorb one or more sizeCategory values, so a thinly-populated
   value (e.g. the single small-medium crossbreed) folds into the nearest brief rather than
   rendering a lonely one-breed group. Data stays accurate per breed; only the display merges. #}
{% set sizeGroups = [
  { keys: ["small", "small-medium"], title: "Toy, Small &amp; Small-Medium Breeds", blurb: "Small mouths, fast metabolisms and a tendency to put on weight — portion control and the right kibble size matter most here. Small-medium crossbreeds sit at the upper end of this brief." },
  { keys: ["medium"], title: "Medium Breeds", blurb: "The biggest group of UK favourites — active, varied, and each with its own dietary quirks." },
  { keys: ["large"], title: "Large Breeds", blurb: "Joint protection and lean growth are the headline concerns; some carry heart-health risks too." },
  { keys: ["giant"], title: "Giant Breeds", blurb: "Controlled, slow growth and careful calcium balance protect developing joints — and appetites are huge." }
] %}

<h1>Best Dog Food by Breed</h1>
<p>Every breed has its own dietary brief — the ear infections a Cocker Spaniel is prone to, the lean growth a Labrador puppy needs, the heart-health watch on a Dobermann. We've reviewed the UK's most popular breeds one by one. Find yours below, grouped by size, with links to puppy and senior feeding guides wherever we've written them.</p>

<p>Not sure where to start? Every breed page recommends specific UK foods for that breed's needs. If you've got a puppy or an older dog, jump straight to the dedicated <strong>Puppy</strong> or <strong>Senior</strong> guide next to the breed — the feeding brief changes a lot at both ends of life.</p>

{% for group in sizeGroups %}
  {% set groupBreeds = [] %}
  {% for breed in breeds %}
    {% if breed.sizeCategory in group.keys %}{% set groupBreeds = (groupBreeds.push(breed), groupBreeds) %}{% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  {% if groupBreeds.length > 0 %}
<h2 id="{{ group.keys[0] }}">{{ group.title | safe }}</h2>
<p>{{ group.blurb | safe }}</p>
<div class="article-list">
  {% for breed in groupBreeds %}
  <div class="article-card">
    <h3><a href="/best-dog-food-for-{{ breed.slug }}/">Best Dog Food for {{ breed.name }}s</a></h3>
    <p>{{ breed.name }}s ({{ breed.weightRange }}, {{ breed.activityLevel }} energy) — key dietary watch-points include {{ breed.commonHealthIssues[0] }}{% if breed.commonHealthIssues[1] %} and {{ breed.commonHealthIssues[1] }}{% endif %}.</p>
    <p>
      <a href="/best-dog-food-for-{{ breed.slug }}/" class="cta">Breed Guide →</a>
      {% if breed.puppyGuide %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ breed.puppyGuide }}">Puppy guide</a>{% endif %}
      {% if breed.seniorGuide %} &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="{{ breed.seniorGuide }}">Senior guide</a>{% endif %}
    </p>
  </div>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

<h2 id="cant-find">Can't Find Your Breed?</h2>
<p>We're adding breeds steadily, prioritising the UK's most popular. If yours isn't here yet, the closest starting point is the food brief for the same size and activity level — or browse our category hubs by need:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="/best-grain-free-dog-food-uk/">Best grain-free dog food</a> — the roundup every breed page draws from</li>
  <li><a href="/best-dog-food-sensitive-stomach-uk/">Best food for sensitive stomachs &amp; skin allergies</a></li>
  <li><a href="/best-puppy-food-uk/">Best puppy food</a> and <a href="/best-senior-dog-food-uk/">best senior dog food</a></li>
  <li><a href="/dog-food-calculator/">Dog food calculator</a> — get a portion estimate for any breed by weight</li>
</ul>

{% block head %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Best Dog Food by Breed UK",
  "description": "Breed-by-breed dog food guides for the UK, grouped by size.",
  "url": "https://pawpicks.co.uk/best-dog-food-by-breed/",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {%- for breed in breeds -%}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "name": "Best Dog Food for {{ breed.name }}s",
        "url": "https://pawpicks.co.uk/best-dog-food-for-{{ breed.slug }}/"
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {%- endfor -%}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}
